      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. every single day it's just more evidence that everything is falling apart and there's nothing anyone can actually do to stop it. it feels like we're all just watching a slow motion train wreck and pretending it's not happening. how are you even supposed to care about building a life or having a future when the world is literally dying?",
